high_descs: Turn to the left and proceed to counter between coffee maker and sink.
Remove coffee mug from coffee maker.
Turn right then left to be in front of sink.
Put mug in left side of sink, turn water on then off, drain sink.  Remove mug from left side of sink.
Turn left, proceed to counter, turn right.
Put mug back on coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Clean mug in sink and return to coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the coffee maker that is on your right. .
Pick up the mug that is sitting on the base of the coffee maker.
Move a bit to your right until you are facing the kitchen sink.
Rinse the mug off in the left sink basin before taking it back out.
Move to your left, back over to the coffee maker.
Put the coffee mug back down on the base of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean mug on the coffee maker base.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn to face your right
Pick up a mug from the coffee maker
Move a step to your right and face the sink
Put the mug in the sink, run the faucet for a few seconds and then pick the cup back up
Move a step to your left so that you are facing the counter
Set the cup back down in the coffee maker
